# Agent Deploy Automation (Kaki Empat v2)

Semua agen **wajib** mengikuti jalur deploy ini. **FTP/SFTP diblokir** — jangan improvisasi upload FTP atau path docroot salah.

## Stack & docroot (jangan salah)

```
Flutter web → api.kakiempat.com (PHP) → MySQL kakiempa_v2
```

| Target | Docroot (relatif `/home/kakiempa/`) |
|--------|--------------------------------------|
| API/BFF | `api.kakiempat.com/` |
| Owner | `owner.kakiempat.com/` |
| Sitter | `sitter.kakiempat.com/` |
| Admin | `admin.kakiempat.com/` |
| Staging | `staging.kakiempat.com/` |
| WWW | `public_html/` |

**Larangan:** `/public_html/api/` — path itu salah.

## Git → cPanel (satu-satunya jalur deploy)

| Komponen | Lokasi | Fungsi |
|----------|--------|--------|
| Instruksi server | `.cpanel.yml` | rsync artefak setelah git pull |
| Skrip server | `scripts/ci/cpanel_deploy.sh` | 6 domain + API |
| Workflow | `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` | Push `main` → `VersionControl/update` |
| Build lokal | `scripts/deploy_git.ps1` | Paket `build/deploy*` untuk commit |
| Picu manual | `scripts/trigger_cpanel_deploy.ps1` | UAPI tanpa menunggu GitHub |

**Secrets GitHub (wajib):** `CPANEL_API_TOKEN`. Opsional: `CPANEL_REPO_PATH` (default `/home/kakiempa/repo_kakiempat`).  
Panduan: `.github/DEPLOY_SECRETS.md`

**Setup cPanel (sekali):** Git™ Version Control → Create repo di `/home/kakiempa/repo_kakiempat` → hubungkan GitHub.

## Alur kerja agen setelah mengubah kode

### Backend PHP (BFF, katalog layanan, payment, booking)

1. Edit di `hosting/api.kakiempat.com/**`
2. Commit — **jangan** stage rahasia (`.mysql_v2.php`, `.agent_telemetry_secret`, `hosting.credentials`)
3. `.\scripts\deploy_git.ps1 -Layer api` → commit `build/deploy_api/` → `git push origin main`
4. Verifikasi: `curl https://www.api.kakiempat.com/health.php`

### Flutter web (owner/sitter/admin/www)

1. `.\scripts\deploy_git.ps1 -Layer web -Target owner -WebRenderer html` (atau `-Layer all`)
2. `git add build/deploy build/deploy_api` → `git push origin main`
3. Money engine penuh: `.\scripts\deploy_owner.ps1 -Layer both -WebRenderer html` lalu push

**Jangan** upload via FTP, WinSCP, atau `SamKirkland/FTP-Deploy-Action`.

## Mata elang — diagnostik mandiri

```http
GET https://www.api.kakiempat.com/health.php
GET https://www.api.kakiempat.com/admin_v2.php?action=agent_health&token=SECRET
```

- Secret server: `.agent_telemetry_secret` — **hanya di server**, jangan commit
- Metrics: booking hari ini, platform fee, DB status, disk

## Prioritas & batasan

- **Money Engine** (`owner_v2.php`) harus stabil — uji sebelum push besar
- Fitur loyalty/community/referral → di belakang `MvpScope` (`lib/core/config/mvp_scope.dart`)
- Query MySQL baru → manfaatkan INDEX (`created_at`, `status`)
- Stack v2 only — no Firebase/FCM/BaaS (lihat `v2-stack-forbidden-services.mdc`)

## Checklist sebelum selesai task deploy

- [ ] Tidak ada rahasia ter-commit
- [ ] Push/workflow Actions hijau
- [ ] `health.php` → `mysql_ok: true`
- [ ] Subdomain target bisa diakses (owner/admin/dll. sesuai scope)
